query:
SELECT a.name as areaName, p.rawAreaText, p.customerRef, h.customerName as hospitalName
FROM areas a
JOIN purchases p ON p.areaId = a.id
JOIN hospitals h ON a.hospitalId = h.id
WHERE p.rawAreaText IS NOT NULL AND p.rawAreaText != ''
ORDER BY h.customerName, a.name
LIMIT 100
